<A>__{they begin walking again..}
<C>__{elizabeth}
<D>__{ever since diana people want glamour and tears..the grand performance..and i'm not very good at that. i prefer to keep my feelings to myself. foolishly i believed that's what people wanted from their queen. not to make a fuss nor wear one's heart on one's sleeve, duty first... self second.}
<A>__{the queen stops..}
<C>__{elizabeth}
<D>__{it's how i was brought up. it's all i've ever known}
